  "texts": [
    "Once the dialogues were created based on specific profiles, GenEvalGPT platform implements several strategies to automatically evaluate the quality of the generated dialogues.",
    "One of those strategies is to extract from the dialogues the profile used for creating them, and compare both the extracted and original profiles.",
    "Then, the efficacy of this profile reconstruction is subsequently evaluated in a second stage using tailored metrics related to both lexical and semantic aspects.",
    "These metrics were Jaccard Index 15, Accuracy, Levenshtein Distance, WER 16, BLEU-1 17, and a cosine similarity metric.",
    "This way, it is possible to check if the generated dialogues followed the requested instructions and included the provided metadata."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "These metrics were Jaccard Index 15, Accuracy, Levenshtein Distance, WER 16, BLEU-1 17, and a cosine similarity metric."
  ]
}